# AI navigation (code map)

Before feature or bug work in this repo:

1. Read root **`AGENTS.md`**.
2. Open **`docs/APPLICATION_MASTER.md` §24** (Feature Location Atlas) and jump to the matching UI / engine / API row.
3. **Do not edit `server/` in this frontend repo** — it is legacy. Canonical API is the sibling **`sync2dine-backend`** (may appear as `tradepro-backend` on GitHub).
4. Prefer domain folders under `src/app/components/`, `engine/`, `config/` over inventing parallel trees.
5. Route catalogue: **`src/app/routeMap.ts`** and trees in **`src/app/routes.tsx`**.
6. Brain aliases: Cynthia = staff UI; Sally = phone staff/sales; Judie = diner phone; Cyrus = legacy widget alias.
7. Persistence SoT is Supabase cloud / live app — not FE localStorage and not backend `server/data/*.json` as primary.
